WEBVTT

1
00:00:05.200 --> 00:00:10.080
I want it to be the first face you saw when you woke up, just like you used to say to me.

2
00:00:10.080 --> 00:00:16.679
I wish that when you were in your sight, the first person you see is me every day.

3
00:00:16.679 --> 00:00:38.179
I woke up at 4 a.m. to drink some water, and I saw a song making breakfast.

4
00:00:38.179 --> 00:00:46.329
So I remember that you liked fried eggs, so I spent a whole month learning how to make

5
00:00:46.329 --> 00:00:48.259
these.

6
00:00:48.259 --> 00:00:56.170
Try it.

7
00:00:56.170 --> 00:00:59.340
Don't bother making this again.

8
00:00:59.340 --> 00:01:01.100
They don't taste like they used to.

9
00:01:01.100 --> 00:01:06.540
Well, we'll leave it past in the past, and look forward to a new future.

10
00:01:06.540 --> 00:01:16.780
I'm afraid Emira can be repaired, but it will still have cracks, just like a human heart.

11
00:01:16.780 --> 00:01:22.379
The beast paid high price to the beauty, so you need to work hard too.

12
00:01:22.379 --> 00:01:23.469
Hold on.

13
00:01:23.469 --> 00:01:28.739
If she's the beauty, who's the beast?

14
00:01:28.739 --> 00:01:29.739
Eat your breakfast.

